com.google.javascript.jscomp

Class TypedVar

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.javascript.jscomp.Var
      • com.google.javascript.jscomp.TypedVar
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StaticTypedRef<JSType>, StaticTypedSlot<JSType>, StaticRef, StaticSlot

    public class TypedVar
extends Var
implements StaticTypedSlot<JSType>, StaticTypedRef<JSType>
    Several methods in this class, such as isVar throw an exception when called. The reason for this is that we want to shadow methods from the parent class, to avoid calling them accidentally.
